{"tid":1965173,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國再爆黑心口罩 黏有死蒼蠅的口罩已透過亞馬遜賣到歐美國家","createTime":"2020-04-09T09:56:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T06:42:36.000Z","uid":75969,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"013af6a535c8fdd62cab09612c424883dcc436e0","tid":1965173,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T09:56:23.000Z","msg":"烏蠅圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2020/04/09/3128433_1.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2F3128433_1.jpg&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVY%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=8c033482\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2F3128433_1.jpg&h=af33d76b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2020/04/09/3128433_1.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n〔編譯盧永山／綜合報導〕中國口罩業者趁武漢肺炎疫情在歐美各國逐漸擴大之際，趕工生產並向重災區銷售口罩，卻被多國發現品質不符標準而遭退貨，並引發全球質疑，中國廠商藉機出售黑心口罩大發災難財。最近有中國網友稱，他向中國口罩業者購買的一批口罩，竟然發現口罩上黏有死蒼蠅，有些口罩上有黑色汙點，而且絶大多數口罩已透過跨境電商平台賣到歐美國家。<br />\n<br />\n一位微博簡介為億恩網創辦人魯泓海的網友稱，3月17日他向河南省滑縣的奧康衛生材料公司購買了35萬個口罩用於出口，由於採購數量巨大，他在驗貨時只能進行抽檢，但在抽檢過程中，竟然發現口罩上粘有死蒼蠅，還有1袋口罩掛耳的帶子上有黑色污漬，另1袋口罩上有多個黑色污點。<br />\n<br />\n魯泓海已將口罩問題報備河南安陽滑縣市場監管局，目前滑縣的民營口罩廠全部被停業整頓。<br />\n<br />\n魯泓海表示，35萬個口罩是在網絡上發起群眾募資活動籌集的資金買的，準備在亞馬遜（Amazon）平台上賣到歐美國家。發現問題後，魯泓海把粘有蒼蠅的口罩影片發給了奧康衛生的負責人，但奧康衛生提出的解決方案是召回新發出的1.3萬個口罩，剩下的口罩一概不賠，而他購買的口罩絕大多數已透過亞馬遜賣到了全世界。<br />\n<br />\n去過滑縣的魯泓海表示，滑縣的慈週寨鎮村子裡有好多小工作坊，村民辦完營業執照後，買台機器就開始生產口罩，還有很多都是在自家房子裡直接做口罩，「哪有什麼衛生條件」？<br />\n<br />\n魯泓海指出，工廠裡的一個工人對他表示，賣給他的那批貨是幾台有問題的機器生產的，那幾台有問題的機器已被賣掉，而那批貨放在角落已經好幾天了。<br />\n<br />\n滑縣教育局指出，奧康衛生3月初向該局捐贈了10萬個口罩，這些口罩將全部轉交滑縣各鄉鎮學校，用於學校做好開學。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3128433\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3128433&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVY%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=309cec3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3128433&h=1695ac13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3128433</a>"},{"pid":"5d2cbaa96e81d0998f1b176c4f69c6d3c14f685e","tid":1965173,"uid":186997,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T09:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/k59zwxy65xc41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2Fk59zwxy65xc41.jpg&h=a9dabfc1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48ff23794c2424b3d0c0602191e8aa4278083a9e","tid":1965173,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T09:59:15.000Z","msg":"係心意"},{"pid":"1ac123c78cc6b96804e537c22c24a395f65dbad2","tid":1965173,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T09:59:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44243fb60a314ed7296fa7410f61a2b444faeca","tid":1965173,"uid":45821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T10:00:26.000Z","msg":"整個銀河系都欠共產黨一句感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855f5ec77b250aa31ebf5579698787af94700b0a","tid":1965173,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T10:00:59.000Z","msg":"抹過鞋底"},{"pid":"a678a5459383911ab7b481c249b0ba45cb6ebcc0","tid":1965173,"uid":237465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T10:11:02.000Z","msg":"免費加料唧, 有冇睇說明書 ?  識唔識睇簡體版本說明書 ?  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1e9533e707f376b53c8e6572dd349ab83fabd3","tid":1965173,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:37:57.000Z","msg":"槍打岀頭鳥，每日都要有屌共新聞"},{"pid":"4ae19254877a4a73b5aef8f474655f270f0316a6","tid":1965173,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d43bc30509fe2b64efcba46be689144874a3b4","tid":1965173,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T06:40:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"094f9ed84e9aaa1eeb44e64c045eee1d8f5e8b0d","tid":1965173,"uid":304856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T06:42:36.000Z","msg":"做好事千瘡百孔；做壞事滴水不漏"}]}